{"questionId":"12255","questionHtml":"<p class=\"indent1\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;\"><strong>Hence</strong>, find the point of intersection of the three planes.</p>\n<p class=\"indent1\" style=\"margin-top:12pt;text-align:center;\"><span class=\"mjpage mjpage__block\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\" alttext=\"\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {x - 3y + z = 1} \\\\   {2x + 2y - z = 2} \\\\   {x - 5y + 3z = 3}  \\end{array}\">\n  <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n    <mtr>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mi>y</mi>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mi>z</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n    </mtr>\n    <mtr>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>y</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mi>z</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n    </mtr>\n    <mtr>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>5</mn>\n          <mi>y</mi>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mi>z</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n    </mtr>\n  </mtable>\n</math></span></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>For attempting to calculate <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  x \\\\   y \\\\   z  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>y</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>z</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> = <em><strong>A</strong></em><sup>−1</sup><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   2 \\\\   3  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x = 1.2{\\text{,}}\\,\\,y = 0.6{\\text{,}}\\,\\,z = 1.6\">\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1.2</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0.6</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>z</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1.6</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;(so the point is (1.2, 0.6, 1.6))&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>&nbsp;A2&nbsp; &nbsp;N2</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"12255","referenceCode":"EXM.1.AHL.TZ0.35b","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Hence, find the point of intersection of the three planes. x − 3 y + z = 1 2 x + 2 y − z = 2 x − 5 y + 3 z = 3","paper":"1","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.14—Introduction to matrices"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}